{"tid":1352680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【荃灣暴力】荃灣辦事處玻璃被擊毀 何君堯：憤怒了","createTime":"2019-07-22T22:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:40:48.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bdfc82285f62ea5bd81bac58aa2b53055be3b1","tid":1352680,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:45:59.000Z","msg":"大批白衣人昨晚在元朗聚集，無差別襲擊市民和西鐵乘客，立法會議員何君堯被拍到與白衣人握手，他其後否認與元朗站襲擊事件有關。其位於荃灣荃豐中心的議員辦事處，下午遭一批示威者在門外貼標語和投擲雞蛋。何君堯其後直言，「憤怒了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gtkmiY8zBZ8GvvqxuVRjZw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190722a202036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgtkmiY8zBZ8GvvqxuVRjZw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190722a202036.jpg&h=f9e17584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君堯晚上7時許，在社交媒體發文，指「憤怒了，今天有一班黑衣暴徒，受到譚凱邦（荃灣區議員）的煽惑下，來到我荃豐中心辦事處進行大肆破壞，不單止是我，我所服務的荃灣區居民也憤怒了，要求將一干人等包括譚凱邦棣捕歸案。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯位於荃灣荃豐中心的議員辦事處，一批示威者下午在門外貼「良心何在」等標語和投擲雞蛋，有市民則在門外的閉路電視上，以便利貼遮擋鏡頭。現時，辦事處的其中一幅玻璃已被擊毀。刑事調查隊（CID）傍晚到現場調查及搜證。"},{"pid":"b9f24e6f34b7dbdeba8b5555d2781f689f01c7b9","tid":1352680,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:46:37.000Z","msg":"自食其果"},{"pid":"7988a0029a6448b56b2ecd546ce7b5632402842f","tid":1352680,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:46:38.000Z","msg":"自己滑倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d35acb718ed4770a1a4da9bb84bfb629e0d62d9","tid":1352680,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:30:10.000Z","msg":"塊玻璃自己跣低架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb014b63b035fd8fce41cbff2a1af3916e595c1d","tid":1352680,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7988a0029a6448